Spec1

the first letter of each input word should be capitalized. For example, "beowulf" will return "Beowulf".

Spec2

For multiple-word titles, the first letter of each word should be capitalized. For "homer's odyssey" we should return "Homer's Odyssey".

Spec3

For titles with small words, those words will not be capitalized. For "return of the king" we return "Return of the King".

Spec4

For titles which start with small words, those words will be capitalized. For "the epic of gilgamesh" we return "The Epic of Gilgamesh".

Spec5

For titles with multiple words, always return a capitalized final word. For "killing in the name of" we return "Killing in the Name Of".
